## Messaging Patterns
Use structured message types. Avoid anonymous string channels. Centralize message enums or builders.

## Coding Standards
- Strict TypeScript
- No silent failures; log meaningful errors
- Avoid blocking the main thread in content scripts

## Branch & Commit Strategy
`feat/*`, `fix/*`, `chore/*`. Conventional Commits. Rebase before PR.

